import { Product } from '../types';

export const products: Product[] = [
  {
    id: '1',
    name: 'üêæ Pet Random Box (1 Pet)',
    description: 'Mystery box containing 1 random pet from Grow a Garden! Includes Common, Uncommon, Rare, Legendary, Mythical, Divine, and Prismatic pets. Each box guarantees at least 1 Rare or higher rarity pet!',
    price: 99.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ff6b6b/ffffff?text=Pet+Random+Box',
    category: 'Pet Boxes',
    stock: 50,
  },
  {
    id: '2',
    name: 'üêæ Pet Random Box (1 Pet)',
    description: 'Premium mystery box containing 1 random pet from Grow a Garden! Higher chance for rare pets. Each box guarantees at least 1 Rare or higher rarity pet!',
    price: 199.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4ecdc4/ffffff?text=Premium+Pet+Box',
    category: 'Pet Boxes',
    stock: 25,
  },
  {
    id: '3',
    name: 'üêæ Pet Random Box (1 Pet)',
    description: 'Ultimate mystery box containing 1 random pet from Grow a Garden! Maximum value with guaranteed rare pets. Each box guarantees at least 1 Rare or higher rarity pet!',
    price: 349.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/45b7d1/ffffff?text=Ultimate+Pet+Box',
    category: 'Pet Boxes',
    stock: 15,
  },
  {
    id: '4',
    name: 'üêæ Pet Random Box (1 Pet)',
    description: 'Legendary mystery box containing 1 random pet from Grow a Garden! The ultimate collection starter. Each box guarantees at least 1 Rare or higher rarity pet!',
    price: 599.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/96ceb4/ffffff?text=Legendary+Pet+Box',
    category: 'Pet Boxes',
    stock: 10,
  },
  {
    id: '5',
    name: 'üé∞ Loot Box Token',
    description: 'Get a chance to win amazing items with our loot box! Try your luck and see what you can win!',
    price: 9.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f9ca24/ffffff?text=Loot+Box+Token',
    category: 'Tokens',
    stock: 100,
  },
  {
    id: '6',
    name: 'üé∞ Loot Box Token Pack (5 Tokens)',
    description: 'Pack of 5 loot box tokens for multiple chances to win!',
    price: 39.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f0932b/ffffff?text=Loot+Box+Token+Pack',
    category: 'Tokens',
    stock: 50,
  },
  {
    id: '7',
    name: 'üé∞ Loot Box Token Pack (10 Tokens)',
    description: 'Pack of 10 loot box tokens for extended gaming fun!',
    price: 69.99,
    image: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/eb4d4b/ffffff?text=Loot+Box+Token+Pack+10',
    category: 'Tokens',
    stock: 30,
  },
];
